// ProjectDeliveryS148 — Sprint 148: localGateMatchesCi (D0047, resolves issue048) — the lightweight
// preventative measure from the Sprint 147 CI failure: make the local pre-commit hook run the FULL
// `keel guard` (all enforced honest-state guards) so the local gate matches CI's `guard all`, instead
// of a curated per-path subset that omitted viewpoint-renderer/etc. EXECUTE (a D0047 correction). 2 pts. AUTONOMOUS (D0049).
